What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: An intensive review (essentially on your own) of all grammatical structures covered up to this point with an emphasis on their presence in complementary literary works.
Helpful and fun course. Some of the ways things are taught (like memorizing vocab for the tests) are not the best ways of learning. However, the class is very good and I would recommend it.
